 Best Setup for You (Optimized Approach)
✅ Step 1: Migrate to WordPress Multisite
Install WordPress Multisite on each VPS.
Import 50 sites per VPS as sub-sites.
✅ Step 2: Assign Designs
Assign one theme per 10 sites.
✅ Step 3: Manage Posts
By default, posts remain separate per site.
Use Global Feed Plugin if you want one unified blog feed.
✅ Step 4: Deploy Static Sites
Use Simply Static (Free: one at a time, Pro: batch mode).
Deploy static files to Cloudflare Pages.
